{"tid":1119564,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"冇下次 唔會再食 祝老闆長做長有！","createTime":"2019-04-22T04:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T09:13:17.000Z","uid":227029,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1d7c39f0e118dbb2a6ab85700e4e15acf0ec6f","tid":1119564,"uid":227029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"今日難得最後一日假，咁就諗住起身落去間新開嘅茶記試下，慢慢嘆個早餐啦，因為見佢都幾抵食&hellip;<br />\n咁我就叫咗個雪菜肉絲米，dllm，嚟到個樣已經有啲麻麻地，諗住算啦賣相差啲啫，味道應該都ok嘅，點知一入口，成陣煙頭溝水味，好撚臭&hellip; <br />\n我就同個阿姐講，佢老鹵態度差撚到，之後夠膽死同我講啲肉係咁，佢地都係咁食&hellip; 之後我一直都keep住好聲好氣叫佢幫我換個另一個早餐，佢黑鳩我面，幫我收走咗之後都眼啤啤&hellip;  嘩，興撚到我呀，好似我唔啱咁，啲味咁撚怪唔撚係要我食落去呀？<br />\n呢間野唔撚再食，已經blacklist&hellip;<br />\n各位巴絲唔撚好再中伏！<br />\n最後祝老闆你長做長有，員工幫你做多啲生意呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e274e46b37fab83162ab60e483a978b632e0881","tid":1119564,"uid":77092,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5eb5dafddd47f0fff7eac1736b0291bd86cb8e83","tid":1119564,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"156b58edd579717f7f329693bd37b06c5b68b1b7","tid":1119564,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"邊間啊？"},{"pid":"9d94624ba9cb7602722955b4f739fb8beff7c587","tid":1119564,"uid":125654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a51149d0aac04a752ccd69e932d0d9eaf4b6aa3","tid":1119564,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:32:14.000Z","msg":"煙頭水浸住豆腐都夠膽賣比人<br />\n有咩過期肉唔敢賣<br />\n反正你地食完最多咪屙 死唔去既"},{"pid":"510a7ae17db7cdf991c59ccc4292c6af3dc5f02e","tid":1119564,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:42:32.000Z"